channel.title: [RS2][SRL] Goblin Scheduler 0.35
channel.description:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [CENTER] [B] SRL2.2 NEW Goblin Scheduler 0.35[/B][/CENTER]
[CENTER] [B] By WT-Fakawi[/B][/CENTER] [CENTER]060606[/CENTER] -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[center][size=12pt] [b]Get rid of your default Lvl-3 's! Prepare to wield a proper Pickaxe![/b][/size][/center]
Here is GoblinKiller revisited! A Total Revamp of Big Bang SRL Script #1 and in fact -as some of you may know- indeed based off my very [b]first [/b]script I released at Kaitnieks, now exactly 11 month ago.
Revamp was necessary since nothing is certain anymore with the new RS-Engine...
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This script will kill Goblins NE of Lumbridge Castle at the Goblin House, thus effectively training your Combat. If your Player dies, [i] -DON'T PANIC- [/i], because the next Player will log in and walk back from Lumbridge Castle to the Goblins [B]ad infinitum[/B]. The script is designed to let your Players die, thus skipping all the troubles other autofighter go through keeping your Players alive.
I hope you like it. Send Bugs, Progress Reports, Screenies to this thread. TIA
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [CENTER] [B] Instructions.[/B][/CENTER] ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 1. Use Runescape Client Low Detail. 2. Set your Screen to 32 bit TRUE color. 3. Position your Low level Players at Lumbridge Castle Gate OR at Goblin House. 4. Equip your Player with[B] no more than 3 wieldable (or wearable) items[/B] (or place them in first three inventory slots) e.g. Sword, Shield and Platebody. 5. Make sure Auto-Retaliate is ON.
Set these variables if needed:
[php]const StartPlayer = 7; const PlayerTime = 1200; // Time for Each Player In Seconds. const RandomPlayerTime = 450; // Random Amount added to PlayerTime const FAWKIDebug = False; // set True if you want Debug Reports const GoblinTimeOut = 10000; // milliseconds before clicking next goblin. const AutoLevels = True ; // Set True to even Skills (Recommended...) const PickupAny = True; // If you want the Script to Pick up Anything [/php]
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [CENTER] [B]Features.[/B][/CENTER] ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- - Will run round the clock with sufficient Players. - SRL 2.2 Based. - Auto evens your skills (Default) or User Selectable Attack Style. - Auto Handling Randoms. - Auto Anything Picker/Bone picker/burier. No, I will not make that optional. - All timed Loops. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [CENTER] [B] Known Issues.[/B][/CENTER] ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- - None. Fast in fighting, but as result little laggy.... - Prepare for some heavy Leo Solving :) ( Look at the bright side: Player with Full zombie :) ) - Yes, eventually your Players [b]will [/b]go astray. They always do. No script is perfect. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [CENTER][B]Version History:[/B][/CENTER] ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- v 0.35 - Revamp based of SRL Rev 222+ from old ScarScape script...
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [CENTER][B]General Notice:[/B][/CENTER] -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Use this script at your own risk. I'm NOT responsible for any Ban or Loss you might encounter using this script.
[LIST] [*]Scar Resource Library 2.2 [*]NAME : Goblin Scheduler 0.35 [*]WRITER : WT-Fakawi [*]CATEGORY : Fighting [*]DESCRIPTION : Kills Goblins at Goblinhouse NE of Lumby Castle [*]USAGE : Start at Lumbridge Castle Square or at Goblin House. [*]AUTOCOLOR :Yes. [*] NOTES : Revamp based off First SRL-script to be published. [/LIST]
[center][b]For Questions: Refer to the SRL Manual provided with the SRL - Include. [/b][/center]
First Progress Report with 12 Noobs: six Players at Zombie Random.
<============== -SRL 2.2 - 0.34- Progress Report ===============> Worked for 21 Hours, 16 Minutes and 55 Seconds Attacked 3430 Goblins.
